				<h4>Green Leafy Vegetables</h4>
				<p>Green leafy vegetables have always been the major source of nutrition. Vegetables like broccoli, peas, capsicum, spinach and other seasonal variants are a great source of vitamin C, healthy fats, fibres and iron. If you are already recovering from the infection, having broth and soup would make recovery easier for you.</p>
