				<p>Fruits offer you a dose of healthy glucose, dietary fibre, vitamin C and many antiviral nutrients. Also, citrus fruits like oranges, grapes, help hydrate the body. Staying hydrated is very important if you are hoping to avoid this infection or fight the symptoms. Including fruits in your daily snacks helps to keep your hunger pangs at bay and provide you with immunity-boosting nutrients.</p>
